---
import Section from "../../../components/Section.astro";
import NewBeginning from "../../../components/icons/new-beginning.svg";
---

<Section containerClass="">
  <div class="flex flex-col items-center">
    <p class="z-10 text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-serif-accent min-h-dvh flex items-center">
      <span class="text-center">Sin embargo...</span>
    </p>
    <p class="z-10 text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-serif-accent min-h-dvh flex items-center">
      <span class="text-center">Hay una cosa que quiero decirte.</span>
    </p>
    <p class="z-10 text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-serif-accent min-h-dvh flex items-center">
      <span class="text-center">Y es que... Cuando te sientas perdido...</span>
    </p>
    <p class="z-10 text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-serif-accent min-h-dvh flex flex-col items-center">
      <span class="text-center">O simplemente quieras dar el siguiente paso...</span>
      <NewBeginning width={100} height={100} class="w-full h-full object-cover" />
    </p>
    <p class="z-10 text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-serif-accent min-h-dvh flex items-center justify-center">
      <span class="text-center">
        Puedes <a class="underline text-accent" target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://www.instagram.com/psic_merrle_gomez/" >buscarme</a>.
      </span>
    </p>
    <p class="z-10 text-3xl xl:text-4xl font-serif-accent min-h-dvh flex items-center">
      <span class="text-center">Yo estaré <a class="underline text-accent" target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer" href="https://wa.me/526861878075?text=Hola!%20Vi%20la%20página%20y%20me%20gustaría%20agendar%20una%20cita">aquí</a> para ayudarte.</span>
    </p>
</Section>